msgstr "(un-)lock"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1274
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <quote>log</quote> command"
msgstr "L'ordre «log»"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1275
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Log command displays a dialog containing the log of the given &URL;. With "
"subversion 1.2 or above it accepts a limit, &ie; how many entries it has to "
"display."
msgstr ""
"L'ordre «log» mostra un diàleg que conté el registre de l'&URL; indicat. Amb "
"el Subversion 1.2 o posterior, aquesta accepta un límit, &ead;, el nombre "
"d'entrades que s'han de mostrar."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1278
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Inside that dialog you may select log entries and get the differences "
"between them."
msgstr ""
"Dins d'aquest diàleg podreu seleccionar les entrades de registre i obtenir "
"les diferències entre elles."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1281
#, no-c-format
msgid "Display the last 20 commit logs"
msgstr "Visualitza el registre de les últimes 20 comissions"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:1282
#, no-c-format
msgid "kdesvn exec log -l 20 -r HEAD&#058;1 myfile.c"
msgstr "kdesvn exec log -l 20 -r HEAD&#058;1 meu_fitxer.c"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1283
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Beware of order of revision: You want go from HEAD to START for the LAST "
"one. So you must give revision HEAD as starting point, otherwise you would "
"get the first 20 entries."
msgstr ""
"Compte amb l'ordre de les revisions: Voleu anar des de HEAD al començament "
"cap a l'últim. Per tant, haureu d'indicar la revisió HEAD com a punt de "
"partida, en cas contrari podríeu obtenir les primeres 20 entrades."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1289
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <quote>diff</quote> command"
msgstr "L'ordre «diff»"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1290
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You get differences between revisions of an item or between two items inside "
"same working copy or repository. When diff'ing revisions of an item, "
"revisions may be given as <option>-r <replaceable>STARTREV</replaceable>:"
"<replaceable>ENDREV</replaceable></option>. When diffing an item inside a "
"working copy without any revisions it prints the diff against repository."
msgstr ""
"Obtindreu les diferències entre les revisions d'un element o entre dos "
"elements dins de la mateixa còpia de treball o repositori. Quan feu el diff "
"en les revisions d'un element, les revisions es poden indicar com <option>-r "
"<replaceable>revisió_inici</replaceable>:<replaceable>revisió_final</"
"replaceable></option>. Quan feu el diff d'un element dins d'una còpia de "
"treball sense cap revisió, es mostrarà el diff contra el repositori."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1293
#, no-c-format
msgid "Print difference against repository, &ie; local changes"
msgstr "Mostra la diferència contra el repositori, &ead;, els canvis locals"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:1294
#, no-c-format
msgid "kdesvn exec diff myfile.c"
msgstr "kdesvn exec diff meu_fitxer.c"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1297
#, no-c-format
msgid "Print difference between revisions"
msgstr "Mostra la diferència entre revisions"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:1298
#, no-c-format
msgid "kdesvn exec diff -r 21:20 myfile.c"
msgstr "kdesvn exec diff -r 21:20 meu_fitxer.c"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1301
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When diffing two items revisions may be appended to &URL; of items. &eg;:"
msgstr ""
"Quan es diferencien dues revisions dels elements, poden afegir-se a l'&URL; "
"dels elements. &pex;:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:1303
#, no-c-format
msgid "http://server/path/item?rev=HEAD"
msgstr "http://servidor.org/camí/element?rev=HEAD"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1305
#, no-c-format
msgid "Diffing two tagged versions"
msgstr "Diferencia dues versions etiquetades"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:1306
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"kdesvn exec diff http://www.alwins-world.de/repos/kdesvn/tags/rel_0_6_2 "
"http://www.alwins-world.de/repos/kdesvn/tags/rel_0_6_3"
msgstr ""
"kdesvn exec diff http://www.alwins-world.de/repos/kdesvn/tags/rel_0_6_2 "
"http://www.alwins-world.de/repos/kdesvn/tags/rel_0_6_3"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1314
#, no-c-format
msgid "Settings"
msgstr "Arranjament"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1315
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Settings can be changed from the setup dialog. They are separated into some "
"subdialogs."
msgstr ""
"Les opcions de configuració es poden canviar des del diàleg de configuració. "
"Estan separades en alguns subdiàlegs."

