#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1337
#, no-c-format
msgid "Items sorting order is case sensitive"
msgstr "L'ordre dels elements distingeix majúscules i minúscules"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1338
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the sort order in main window is case sensitive or not, &ie; if <quote>a</"
