#. Tag: trans_comment
#: index.docbook:2247
#, no-c-format
msgid "CREDIT_FOR_TRANSLATORS"
msgstr "<para>Traductor de la documentació: &credits.Antoni.Bella;</para>"

#. Tag: chapter
#: index.docbook:2247
#, no-c-format
msgid "&underFDL; &underGPL;"
msgstr "&underFDL; &underGPL;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2254
#, no-c-format
msgid "Syntax for revisions"
msgstr "Sintaxi per a les revisions"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2255
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Revisions may be given in the same form as for the standard "
"<application>svn</application> client. That means: number, keyword or date."
msgstr ""
"Les revisions es poden indicar en la mateixa forma que per al client "
"<application>svn</application> estàndard. Això vol dir: número, paraula clau "
"o data."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2262
#, no-c-format
msgid "Number"
msgstr "Número"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2263
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A number greater or equal -1. -1 means <quote>unspecified revision</quote>, "
"0 is the beginning. Normally, these numbers should not be used (most "
"operations will fail with that)."
msgstr ""
"Un número més gran o igual que -1. El -1 significa «revisió sense "
"especificar», 0 és el començament. Normalment, aquests números no s'han "
"d'utilitzar (la majoria de les operacions fallaran)."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2269
#, no-c-format
msgid "Keyword"
msgstr "Paraula clau"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2270
#, no-c-format
msgid "One of"
msgstr "Un de"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2274
#, no-c-format
msgid "HEAD"
msgstr "HEAD"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2278
#, no-c-format
msgid "BASE"
msgstr "BASE"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2282
#, no-c-format
msgid "COMMITED"
msgstr "COMMITED"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2286
#, no-c-format
msgid "PREV"
msgstr "PREV"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2290
#, no-c-format
msgid "START"
msgstr "START"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2294
#, no-c-format
msgid "WORKING"
msgstr "WORKING"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2301
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The keywords are case sensitive! For example, head is not the same as HEAD."
msgstr ""
"Les paraules clau distingeixen majúscules i minúscules! Per exemple, «head» "
"no és el mateix que «HEAD»."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2308
#, no-c-format
msgid "Date"
msgstr "Data"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2309
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Date in form {YYYY-MM-DD}. It must real MM or DD - &eg; 2005-1-1 must be "
"written as {2005-01-01}."
msgstr ""
"Data en la forma {AAAA-MM-DD}. Els MM o DD seran reals - &pex; 2005-1-1 s'ha "
"d'escriure com {2005-01-01}-."

# skip-rule: t-sp_in
#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2317
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Appending a specific revision to an &URL; will always made via <quote>?"
"rev=<replaceable>revision</replaceable></quote>."
msgstr ""
"En afegir una revisió específica a un &URL; sempre es farà «?"
"rev=<replaceable>revisió</replaceable>»."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "KIO::ksvn::special knows the following operations, these are made almost "
#~ "equal in call to the current existing in KIO from kdesdk-kioslaves so, "
#~ "for instance, &kdevelop; may use it if kdesdk-kioslaves isn't installed "
#~ "but uses &kdesvn;::KIO::svn."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "El KIO::ksvn::special coneix les següents operacions, aquestes es fan "
#~ "gairebé igual que les crides existents al KIO del kdesdk-kioslaves, per "
#~ "exemple, el &kdevelop; pot utilitzar-lo si el kdesdk-kioslaves no es "
#~ "troba instal·lat. Utilitzarà &kdesvn;::KIO::svn."
